column3: With this fish in your tank, loss of health will not occur due to starvation.
With this fish in your tank, sick fish have a better chance of being cured.
With this fish in your tank, young fish tend to grow more rapidly.
With this fish in your tank, pregnant fish will produce an extra baby.
The golden guppy of Isola has been reborn! This legendary fish will certainly make you a rich breeder.
